txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Coarse skins from beasts to the north of Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'I can make good use of these. Thank you.'
'We need to repair a lot of items, shoes, straps, and the like. If you can get coarse skin from the tougher beasts north of Amon Raith, I can fix much of what we still have.'
Rangers of Esteld√≠n Task: Coarse Skins
Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of coarse skins.
Deliver the coarse skins to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
You have accepted a task to deliver coarse skins to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith in the North Downs. You can find the coarse skins from the beasts to the north of the ruin of Amon Raith.
Wanted: Coarse skins from beasts to the north of Amon Raith.
